Perhaps it&amp;#39;s &amp;#39;ou&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;lx&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;xz&amp;#39;, and there is no extra &amp;#39;x&amp;#39;.

Maybe I miswrote.

Wait, let&amp;#39;s write the letters as they come:

